'''俄亥俄州立大学莱马校区'''（{{lang-en|Ohio State University at Lima}}）是[[俄亥俄州立大学|俄亥俄州立大学]]设在[[莱马_(俄亥俄州)|莱马]]的校区。校区占地{{convert|565|acre|km2|sing=on}}，北距[[托莱多_(俄亥俄州)|托莱多]]{{convert|80|mi|km}}。该校区提供140门课程和12个本科文理学士学位，其中有十个学位为四年制项目，另两个项目为专升本项目。<ref name="majors">{{cite web | title = Academic Programs | url = http://lima.osu.edu/admissions/bachelors.php | accessdate = 2012-08-29 | publisher = The Ohio State University at Lima | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121114101221/http://lima.osu.edu/admissions/bachelors.php | archivedate = 2012-11-14 }}</ref> 超过170个专业的学生可以在莱马校区开始自己的学业，并在哥伦布主校区毕业。莱马校区有超过20个学生社团，另有12个校内体育俱乐部。<ref name="ClubsOrgs">{{cite web | title = Student Life: Student Organizations and Clubs | url = http://lima.osu.edu/students/studentclubs.php | accessdate = 2012-08-29 | publisher = The Ohio State University at Lima | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120828054019/http://lima.osu.edu/students/studentClubs.php | archivedate = 2012-08-28 }}</ref><ref name="Intramurals">{{cite web | title = Athletics: Barons Intramural Sports | url = http://lima.osu.edu/athletics/intramurals.php | accessdate = 2012-08-29 | publisher = The Ohio State University at Lima | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120909113628/http://lima.osu.edu/athletics/intramurals.php | archivedate = 2012-09-09 }}</ref>

莱马校区图书馆共有藏书76,000卷以及200份期刊。图书馆的线上数据库另可提供数千种期刊的内容。<ref>{{cite web | title = About the Library | url = http://lima.osu.edu/library/about.php | accessdate = 2012-08-30 | publisher = The Ohio State University at Lima | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130102004456/http://lima.osu.edu/library/about.php | archivedate = 2013-01-02 }}</ref><!--The University shares the campus with [[James_A._Rhodes_State_College|James A. Rhodes State College]].<ref name="HistCent">{{cite web|url=http://www.ohiohistorycentral.org/entry.php?rec=2522|title=James A. Rhodes State College|date=2006-07-12|publisher=Ohio History Central|accessdate=2008-11-08}}</ref>
